  <brief_title>Pragmatic Trial Comparing Symptom-Oriented Versus Routine Stress Testing in High-Risk Patients Undergoing Percutaneous Coronary Intervention</brief_title>
  <acronym>POST PCI</acronym>
  <official_title>a Multi-center, Open-label, Nationwide Registry-based, Randomized, Pragmatic Trial Comparing 2 Post-PCI Management Strategies in High-risk PCI Patients With Complex Clinical and Lesion Characteristics</official_title>
